},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Moreover, remember that there was a “Done” list in my weekly board? That also does something\nspecial. I have a BFT link that, whenever clicked, does the following:","position":{"start":{"line":100,"column":1},"end":{"line":100,"column":1}},"key":"Vc754B64Zq"}],"key":"ZPPtjnQ7Y2"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":103,"column":1},"end":{"line":107,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":103,"column":1},"end":{"line":103,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Loop through every card in the “Done” list","position":{"start":{"line":103,"column":1},"end":{"line":103,"column":1}},"key":"KsElhoBXy1"}],"key":"otqwR75aU6"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":104,"column":1},"end":{"line":104,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"For each card, find the Board ID that represents the board the card came from","position":{"start":{"line":104,"column":1},"end":{"line":104,"column":1}},"key":"Lm8MrbyB3t"}],"key":"v0EgUBbUiJ"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":105,"column":1},"end":{"line":107,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Move the card to that board, put it in a “Done” list that is automatically created using the\nnumber of the current active week.","position":{"start":{"line":105,"column":1},"end":{"line":105,"column":1}},"key":"RXjyUAXoAR"}],"key":"Ao720qD4WZ"}],"key":"ePyUUYHi7m"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":108,"column":1},"end":{"line":108,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"So, the general flow of cards through this system looks like this:","position":{"start":{"line":108,"column":1},"end":{"line":108,"column":1}},"key":"Pb1Tk1fQZA"}],"key":"iwobGi3uMV"},{"type":"list","ordered":true,"start":1,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":110,"column":1},"end":{"line":120,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"po